{"tid":2487913,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"學車新手一問","createTime":"2021-04-14T01:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T04:20:14.000Z","uid":233059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe6209ce2161e6eda6d19180d7c2dfaf4fde9b9","tid":2487913,"uid":233059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T01:46:32.000Z","msg":"無知一問<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSRvHufRyNgmGhuQEdg2497qxcwiHXmJAwLpKGkuGfa2a?filename=mPJ6LTH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmPJ6LTH.png&h=51458407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅色交叉=行人<br />\n藍色框=車輛<br />\n行人向紅色箭嘴方向行走<br />\n車輛向藍色箭嘴方向前進(非倒車)<br />\n<br />\n噉嘅情況<br />\n1.嗰個位屬唔屬於行人道路呢?<br />\n2.車主係唔係應該要先讓行人過咗再駛前呢?<br />\n<br />\n道閘如圖所示, 係<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">無開閘</span></span><br />\n再根據運輸署道路使用者守則:<br />\n[私家車內觀看行人]<br />\n<br />\n注意行人<br />\n<br />\n無論何時何地，即使行人胡亂橫過馬路，駕駛人在法律上和道義上均有責任，提防和避免撞倒行人。因此，你應該時刻讓路給在馬路上的行人。<br />\n<br />\n在行人眾多的地方，尤其是在擠擁的街道上，或在巴士站或在攤檔附近時，你應小心慢駛。提防有行人突然從已停泊或停定的車輛後面走出馬路。駕駛較寧靜的車輛，例如電動或混合動力車輛時，由於車輛聲量較低，行人可能不察覺你正在駛近，因此尤須小心。<br />\n<br />\n駛入或駛出馬路時，應盡量使用正式的行車通道，避免倒車駛進馬路，並應讓路給行人。<br />\n<br />\n個車主開咹再駛前閘鳩個路人, 甚至屌個路人「癡線」合唔合理?"},{"pid":"e1aa5fd581229964e0fa267daf7752ba689c7731","tid":2487913,"uid":57462,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T01:48:34.000Z","msg":"撞親人幾時都係你輸，你諗你"},{"pid":"1c5b56a600ed5c8683944f3dee564e7f0f3b4b87","tid":2487913,"uid":57462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T01:49:40.000Z","msg":"另外horn 唔係咁用，屌人老母就睇番許賢教學"},{"pid":"98393df33dc9fbf51970035743b5f40867c6f19c","tid":2487913,"uid":233059,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e1aa5fd581229964e0fa267daf7752ba689c7731","tid":2487913,"uid":57462,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T01:48:34.000Z","msg":"撞親人幾時都係你輸，你諗你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T01:49:46.000Z","msg":"我唔係車主,我係路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw,感謝師兄"},{"pid":"1d670ab3921204ff474bc3a3e1f33600b60e7d53","tid":2487913,"uid":119450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:26:57.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\n成日好撚多私家車高速一野轉入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4426b677b4522883d0465e837e4887b3a1423a29","tid":2487913,"uid":233059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d670ab3921204ff474bc3a3e1f33600b60e7d53","tid":2487913,"uid":119450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:26:57.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\n成日好撚多私家車高速一野轉入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:34:45.000Z","msg":"啱呀, 唔係唔俾佢剷上嚟呀, 唔讓行人重要屌鳩人嗰下先癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64a9c193c1d4b1e2b20a53c2860f235736b5369","tid":2487913,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4426b677b4522883d0465e837e4887b3a1423a29","tid":2487913,"uid":233059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d670ab3921204ff474bc3a3e1f33600b60e7d53","tid":2487913,"uid":119450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:26:57.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\n成日好撚多私家車高速一野轉入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:34:45.000Z","msg":"啱呀, 唔係唔俾佢剷上嚟呀, 唔讓行人重要屌鳩人嗰下先癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T04:09:04.000Z","msg":"響安你可以唔理佢, 佢屌你就屌返佢<br />\n<br />\n閘你咪順勢跌低報警玩大佢囉<br />\n<br />\n不過撞著個痴線司機, 輕則斷手斷腳, 重則無命"},{"pid":"4f13e7c1bad075e474545fc8a04aa85db772784b","tid":2487913,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T04:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 